# Minecraft MOD Rules

The Fabric client mod is only responsible for state scanning and survival-legal action execution.

Allowed action categories:
- look
- move
- sneak
- jump
- select hotbar item
- use item
- break reachable block
- place held item
- craft through player-accessible UI
- abort

Forbidden:
- `/give`
- `/fill`
- `/setblock`
- `/tp`
- `/summon`
- `/kill`
- creative-mode-only behavior
- bypassing inventory checks
- continuing after abort

Every action sequence must support cancellation and key release.
